規定？（5 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d71bc30b91f", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "309", "s": "0508", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "就業安全制度", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-8b44517b-moex-00051', 'heelevel3-8b44517b', 'heelevel3-8b44517b-moex-113-1ffb5c63', 'sub-heelevel3-8b44517b-03', NULL, 'essay', '針對建教生之勞動權益，請回答下列問題：
